  <brief_title>Study With Seletracetam (Ucb 44212) in Adult Subjects (18 to 65 Years) With Partial Onset Seizures</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Exploratory, Multicenter, Dose-escalation Study Examining the Efficacy, Safety and Tolerability of Ucb 44212 Used at Doses of 10 mg, 20 mg, 40 mg and 80 mg b.i.d. (Total Daily Dose of 20 to 160 mg) in Adult Subjects (18-65 Years) With Refractory Epilepsy Suffering From Partial Onset Seizures (Whether or Not Secondarily Generalized) and Treated With 1, 2 or 3 Approved Antiepileptic Drugs</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>UCB Pharma</agency>
